name: Jesse Jordan
text: Food is consistently forgotten and I end up waiting twenty minutes with minimal lines, and I have to tell three of the college student workers in order to get what I paid for. Plus the food is horrible in quality, incredibly inconsistent.

name: Erin Miller
text: Food is good but staff messed up my order and when taking it back and asking for the right pizza manager/staff was giving additiude and complaining the whole time the correct pizza was being made.
